<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc17a4b5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2296a–2"><num value="2296a–2">§ 2296a–2.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idbc17a4b6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2296a–2/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated $715,000,000 to carry out this part. The aggregate amount authorized in the preceding sentence shall be increased annually as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s2296a">section 2296a of this title</ref>, based upon an inflation index to be determined by the Secretary.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idbc17a4b7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2296a–2/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Source</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Funds described in subsection (a) shall be provided from the Fund established under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s2297g">section 2297g of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idbc17a4b8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/486/tX/s1003">Pub. L. 102–486, title X, § 1003</ref>, <date date="1992-10-24">Oct. 24, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/2947">106 Stat. 2947</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/104/259/s3/b">Pub. L. 104–259, § 3(b)</ref>, <date date="1996-10-09">Oct. 9, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/3174">110 Stat. 3174</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/105/388/s11/b">Pub. L. 105–388, § 11(b)</ref>, <date date="1998-11-13">Nov. 13, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/3485">112 Stat. 3485</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/107/222/s1/b">Pub. L. 107–222, § 1(b)</ref>, <date date="2002-08-21">Aug. 21, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/1336">116 Stat. 1336</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbc17a4b9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbc17a4ba-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idbc17a4bb-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was enacted as part of the Energy Policy Act of 1992, and not as part of the Atomic Energy Act of 1954 which comprises this chapter.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbc17a4bc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2002—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/107/222">Pub. L. 107–222</ref> substituted “$715,000,000” for “$490,000,000”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1998—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/105/388">Pub. L. 105–388</ref> substituted “$490,000,000” for “$415,000,000”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1996—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/104/259">Pub. L. 104–259</ref> substituted “$415,000,000” for “$310,000,000”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
